{"tid":617827,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【港式奇幻漫畫】《大衛王》第1話","createTime":"2018-04-05T09:44:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T09:46:19.000Z","uid":180575,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"136540c45a94b19bab93fc742539e5ccd4913cda","tid":617827,"uid":180575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T09:44:32.000Z","msg":"我會考Art拎F學人畫漫畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n故事同小學同學共同創作<br />\n<br />\n「大衛王」係愚人節剛推出嘅港式奇幻漫畫，經網絡免費長篇連載，每月第1日推出新1話，第1話係加長版。<br />\n<br />\n貼第1話頭幾頁圖比大家預覽下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/05/174337_25f09b29a750d6d3502fb34d5c5f2dfa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F05%2F174337_25f09b29a750d6d3502fb34d5c5f2dfa.jpg&h=504e3fa1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/05/174338_ee4d7a9f59010d5bc92f7b40f9be0d2b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F05%2F174338_ee4d7a9f59010d5bc92f7b40f9be0d2b.jpg&h=d142f0c1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/05/174339_dcee5b286dc81bcb5b2a13b30a88130c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F05%2F174339_dcee5b286dc81bcb5b2a13b30a88130c.jpg&h=82f387e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n漫畫第1話網址：<br />\n<a href=\"https://continuehk.com/david/episode1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcontinuehk.com%2Fdavid%2Fepisode1%2F&d=nHGlubfLw6K5TswqfdeYR2owyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=9d524d29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://continuehk.com/david/episode1/</a><br />\n<br />\n用Flipbook模擬睇實體漫畫雙頁翻頁效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n新手必看漫畫操作教學：<br />\n<br />\n1.<br />\n模擬看實體日本漫畫感覺，向右翻頁，<br />\n每頁內容由右至左上至下觀看。<br />\n2.<br />\n翻頁操作：<br />\n手指拖動頁面/按左右箭頭掣/按電腦鍵盤左右箭頭掣<br />\n縮放操作：<br />\n兩指縮放/按漫畫下方功能表的兩個放大鏡掣<br />\n3.<br />\n雙頁顯示：<br />\n橫放手機和平板電腦較適合雙頁顯示漫畫。<br />\n4.<br />\n單頁顯示：<br />\n先橫放手機，按漫畫下方功能表最右的齒輪掣，<br />\n選擇Single page，再直放手機就可單頁顯示漫畫。<br />\n平板電腦和電腦隨時都有這個單頁顯示選項。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原FB post網址：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/continuehk/posts/433531227079474\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcontinuehk%2Fposts%2F433531227079474&d=nHGlubfLw6K5TswqfdeYR2owyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=7177f108\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/continuehk/posts/433531227079474</a><br />\n<br />\n請like或follow我FB專頁：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/continuehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcontinuehk&d=nHGlubfLw6K5TswqfdeYR2owyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=62b43850\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/continuehk</a><br />\n可係FB每篇文嘅post留言發表意見<br />\n幫手分享post就更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日後會有更多漫畫相關內容，詳情留意：<br />\n<a href=\"https://continuehk.com/david\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcontinuehk.com%2Fdavid&d=nHGlubfLw6K5TswqfdeYR2owyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=ef54d186\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://continuehk.com/david</a>"},{"pid":"26fa15b7ae924832db6878892848d508e7a4f0b0","tid":617827,"uid":180575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T09:46:19.000Z","msg":"第1話最尾結局入面份報紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/05/174541_2bb96c7ccc077cc7f24739b7ac644352.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F05%2F174541_2bb96c7ccc077cc7f24739b7ac644352.jpg&h=cd16380f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}